title: Victim in Anderson County shooting identified by sheriff's office
content:
After the final review, the case will submitted to the Anderson County district attorney’s office for grand jury review.
The shooting occurred in the 500 block of Anderson County Road 350 about 8:50 p.m. Dec. 23.
Deputies and investigators arrived at the scene and found the victim with a gunshot wound to the head. Several individuals were present when the shooting occurred, according to the news release.
- Anderson County Sheriff’s Office
